How long until you get your new tee?

We use USPS parcel service in the United States, Canada Post and other postage mediums in Canada and many different reputable shipping mediums to all other countries.

Our t-shirts and hooded pullovers are custom made at time of order, so there is some time required to print and dry the shirt or hooded pullover and prepare it for shipping. 
In some cases, it can be processed the same day, but we can't guarantee it. 

All shirts and hooded pullovers are custom made within two to three business days after you place your order.

The average wait times vary for each country. 
We ship USPS and people in the U.S. should expect their shirt or hooded pullover at their door 5-10 business days after processing time. Canada 6-14.  Sometimes, delivery is much sooner than this but we can't guarantee delivery times. It all depends on USPS (who are usually very good). 

International orders can take 3 to 4 weeks to arrive and during busy seasons such as Christmas, even longer.

Once your order is shipped there is a tracking number that you receive via email and can use to track your package (USA only).
International shipments also have tracking information until the package leaves the United States. 
Canadian orders do not have tracking information.
